%20is%20an%20activist%20and%20a%20lawyer.%20The%20two%20are%20accused%20in%20the%20Bhima%20Koregaon%E2%80%93Elgar%20Parishad%3Ca%20data-wpel-link%3D%5C%22internal%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheleaflet.in%2Fcategory%2Fbhima-koregaon%2F%5C%22%3E%C2%A0case%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20charged%20under%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22external%20noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mha.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FA1967-37.pdf%5C%22%20data-wpel-link%3D%5C%22external%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A0Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%2C%201967%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0(UAPA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20had%20been%20incarcerated%20for%20almost%20five%20years%20without%20a%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20conditions%20of%20the%20bail%2C%20the%20duo%20were%20required%20not%20to%20change%20their%20mobile%20phones%2C%20keep%20their%20phones%20charged%20at%20all%20times%2C%20keep%20the%20location%20status%20of%20the%20phones%20%E2%80%98active%E2%80%99%20all%20through%20the%20day%2C%20and%20pair%20the%20devices%20with%20the%20devices%20of%20the%20investigating%20office%20of%20the%20NIA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20harsh%20bail%20conditions%20did%20nothing%20to%20protect%20the%20right%20of%20the%20duo%20to%20a%20minimal%20level%20of%20privacy%2C%20as%20the%20bail%20conditions%20intend%20to%20keep%20the%20duo%20tethered%20to%20the%20authorities%20at%20all%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bail%20conditions%20were%20perhaps%20also%20an%20indirect%20recognition%20of%20the%20commonplace%20notion%20that%20mobile%20phones%20are%20used%20as%20surveillance%20tools%20by%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20an%20NIA%20special%20court%20of%20judge%20Rajesh%20Katari%20heard%20the%20difficulty%20faced%20by%20the%20NIA%20in%20complying%20with%20the%20bail%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20issue%20of%20non-compliance%20with%20the%20bail%20condition%20of%20pairing%20devices%2C%20the%20court%20suggested%20installation%20of%20applications%20that%20can%20assist%20in%20pairing%20and%20tracking%20the%20devices%20on%20the%20mobile%20phones%20of%20the%20accused%20and%20the%20NIA%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20this%2C%20the%20counsel%20representing%20the%20NIA%20raised%20concerns%20about%20the%20possible%20infringement%20of%20privacy%20of%20the%20concerned%20investigating%20officers%20of%20the%20NIA%20if%20the%20devices%20were%20to%20be%20paired.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20does%20the%20law%20say%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20held%20in%20the%20case%20of%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22external%20noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F127517806%2F%5C%22%20data-wpel-link%3D%5C%22external%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A0%3Ci%3EJustice%20K.S.%20Puttaswamy%20and%20Another%20versus%20Union%20of%20India%20and%20Others%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0(2017)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20right%20to%20privacy%20is%20protected%20by%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22external%20noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F1199182%2F%5C%22%20data-wpel-link%3D%5C%22external%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A0Article%2021%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0(protection%20of%20life%20and%20personal%20liberty)%20of%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22external%20noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F1445510%2F%5C%22%20data-wpel-link%3D%5C%22external%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESection%205(2)%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0of%20the%20Indian%20Telegraph%20Act%2C%201885%20allows%20electronic%20tapping%20and%20interception%20under%20certain%20conditions%2C%20including%20on%20the%20occurrence%20of%20public%20emergency%2C%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20public%20safety%20and%20for%20preventing%20incitement%20to%20the%20commission%20of%20an%20offence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20case%20of%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22external%20noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F31276692%2F%5C%22%20data-wpel-link%3D%5C%22external%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A0%3Ci%3EPeople%E2%80%99s%20Union%20for%20Civil%20Liberties%20versus%20Union%20of%20India%20and%20others%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0(1996)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20held%20that%20interception%20of%20telephones%20and%20wiretaps%20was%20a%20serious%20invasion%20of%20privacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20mobile%20phone%20tracking%20remains%20a%20grey%20area%20around%20the%20globe.%20In%20July%202018%2C%20the%20United%20States%20Supreme%20Court%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22external%20noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fdoes-tracking-mobile-location-breach-privacy-5241556%2F%5C%22%20data-wpel-link%3D%5C%22external%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emandated%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0a%20warrant%20for%20tracking%20a%20suspect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20did%20the%20court%20say%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20court%20directed%20the%20NIA%20to%20conduct%20a%20thorough%20verification%20of%20the%20bail%20conditions.%20It%20also%20directed%20the%20NIA%20to%20apprise%20the%20court%20of%20the%20difficulties%20in%20complying%20with%20the%20bail%20conditions%20on%20the%20next%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%20court%20observed%20that%20if%20the%20NIA%20is%20not%20able%20to%20meet%20the%20bail%20conditions%2C%20it%20will%20have%20to%20approach%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20seek%20modifications%20of%20the%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20is%20posted%20for%20hearing%20on%20the%20plea%20of%20the%20accused%20persons%20for%20the%20NIA%20to%20comply%20with%20Section%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22external%20noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F1613898%2F%5C%22%20data-wpel-link%3D%5C%22external%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A0207%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0(supply%20to%20the%20accused%20of%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20police%20report%20and%20other%20documents)%20of%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%20(CrPC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20previous%20hearings%2C%20the%20accused%20persons%20had%20raised%20the%20grievance%20that%20despite%20filing%20several%20applications%20with%20the%20investigating%20authorities%20under%20Section%20207%20of%20the%20CrPC%2C%20they%20had%20not%20been%20allowed%20access%20to%20the%20compact%20disks%2C%20which%20are%20an%20important%20piece%20of%20evidence%20furnished%20by%20the%20NIA%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20will%20be%20further%20heard%20on%20September%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBackground%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20connection%20with%20the%20Elgar%20Parishad%E2%80%93Bhima%20Koregaon%20case%2C%20on%20June%206%2C%202018%2C%20Pune%20police%20arrested%20human%20rights%20lawyer%20and%20Dalit%20rights%20activist%2C%20Surendra%20Gadling%3B%20Dalit%20rights%20activist%20and%20editor%20of%20the%20Marathi%20magazine%3Ci%3E%C2%A0Vidrohi%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20Sudhir%20Dhawale%3B%20activist%20and%20researcher%2C%20and%20member%20of%20the%20Committee%20for%20the%20Release%20of%20Political%20Prisoners%2C%20Rona%20Wilson%3B%20former%20head%20of%20the%20English%20department%20at%20Nagpur%20University%2C%20and%20Dalit%20and%20women%E2%80%99s%20rights%20activist%2C%20Shoma%20Sen%3B%20and%20forest%20rights%20activist%20and%20former%20fellow%20of%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Rural%20Development%20Fellowship%20Programme%20of%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Rural%20Development%2C%20Mahesh%20Raut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2028%2C%202018%2C%20activist%2C%20poet%2C%20writer%20and%20teacher%20Varavara%20Rao%3B%20trade%20unionist%2C%20activist%20and%20lawyer%2C%3Ca%20data-wpel-link%3D%5C%22internal%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheleaflet.in%2Fbhima-koregaon-case-bombay-hc-grants-default-bail-to-sudha-bharadwaj-but-declines-the-same-to-eight-other-accused%2F%5C%22%3E%C2%A0Sudha%20Bharadwaj%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20Arun%20Ferreira%3B%20Vernon%20Gonsalves%3B%20and%20human%20rights%20activist%20and%20jou