eight%3D%5C%223334%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIthaca%2C%20New%20York%20last%20year%20became%20the%20first%20city%20where%20Starbucks%20workers%20successfully%20unionized%20at%20all%20of%20the%20city's%20Starbucks%20locations.%3Cp%3ELindsay%20DeDario%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECornell%20University%20will%20no%20longer%20serve%20Starbucks%20coffee%20on%20campus%20following%20student%20protests.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EStudents%20say%20Starbucks%20engaged%20in%20illegal%20union-busting%20when%20it%20closed%20every%20store%20in%20Ithaca%2C%20New%20York.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELabor%20experts%20say%20this%20worker-student%20coalition%20could%20be%20a%20winning%20strategy%20for%20Starbucks%20organizers.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECornell%20University%20said%20this%20week%20it%20would%20not%20renew%20its%20vendor%20contract%20with%20Starbucks%20after%20students%20protested%20the%20coffee%20chain's%20response%20to%20unionization%20efforts.%20Labor%20experts%20say%20it%20could%20be%20a%20turning%20point%20for%20the%20Starbucks%20union.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20more%20than%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstories.starbucks.com%2Fpress%2F2022%2Fstarbucks-enters-new-era-of-growth-driven-by-an-unparalleled-reinvention-plan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E9%2C000%20company-operated%20stores%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Starbucks%20is%20the%20largest%20coffee%20company%20in%20the%20country.%C2%A0%20Starbucks%20employees%20at%20more%20than%20300%20stores%20across%20the%20nation%20have%20successfully%20unionized%20under%20Starbucks%20Workers%20United%20since%202021%2C%20joining%20employees%20at%20national%20companies%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funion-leaders-at-amazon-starbucks-target-trader-joes-wells-fargo-2022-9%5C%22%3Elike%20Trader%20Joe's%20and%20Amazon%3C%2Fa%3E%20making%20similar%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20current%20contract%20between%20Cornell%20and%20Starbucks%20lasts%20until%202025%2C%20university%20officials%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20it%20would%20%26quot%3Binitiate%20an%20inclusive%20process%26quot%3B%20to%20select%20a%20new%20coffee%20vendor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20came%20after%20Cornell%20students%20claimed%20Starbucks'%20decision%20to%20close%20all%20three%20stores%20in%20Ithaca%20after%20workers%20voted%20to%20unionize%20was%20an%20act%20of%20illegal%20union-busting.%20Student%20activist%20Danielle%20Donovan%20told%20Insider%20that%20students%20wrote%20a%20formal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fassembly.cornell.edu%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fsa_r1_starbucks_off_our_campus_2.pdf%5C%22%3Eresolution%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20May%20calling%20for%20the%20end%20of%20the%20partnership%20and%C2%A0staged%20a%20sit-in%20at%20Cornell's%20administrative%20building.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAndrew%20Trull%2C%20a%20Starbucks%20spokesperson%2C%20said%20Starbucks%20officials%20respect%20the%20rights%20of%20their%20employees%20to%20unionize%20and%20are%20committed%20to%20engaging%20in%20good-faith%20collective%20bargaining.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStarbucks%20trains%20managers%20that%20no%20partner%20will%20be%20disciplined%20for%20engaging%20in%20lawful%20union%20activity%20and%20that%20there%20will%20be%20no%20tolerance%20for%20any%20unlawful%20anti-union%20behavior%2C%26quot%3B%20Trull%20wrote%20to%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStudent%20efforts%20to%20end%20the%20partnership%20is%20a%20promising%20strategy%20for%20union%20organizers%2C%20according%20to%20Johnnie%20Kallas%2C%20a%20Ph.D.%20student%20and%20director%20of%20Cornell%20University's%20Labor%20Action%20Tracker%2C%20a%20database%20designed%20to%20track%20strikes%20and%20labor%20protests%20across%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20obstacles%20facing%20the%20Starbucks%20campaign%20is%20how%20to%20generate%20adequate%20pressure%20to%20bring%20Starbucks%20to%20the%20table%20for%20negotiations.%20One%20strategy%20they've%20tried%20is%20striking%2C%20but%20Starbucks%20is%20so%20huge%20and%20has%20so%20much%20financial%20power.%20So%C2%A0they%20need%20to%20think%20of%20other%20ways%20to%20generate%20pressure%2C%26quot%3B%20Kallas%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20this%20is%20a%20really%20great%20example.%20This%20can%20make%20a%20meaningful%20impact%20on%20Starbucks%20and%20move%20them%20toward%20contract%20negotiations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJaz%20Brisack%2C%20a%20former%20Starbucks%20barista%20and%20organizer%20with%20Workers%20United%2C%20an%20umbrella%20union%20that%20includes%C2%A0Starbucks%20Workers%20United%2C%20said%20the%20student%20activism%20at%20Cornell%20could%20be%20a%20new%20way%20for%20workers%20to%20seek%20accountability.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20shows%20what%20students%20and%20Starbucks%20workers%20demanding%20accountability%20can%20look%20like%2C%26quot%3B%20Brisack%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20start%20of%20a%20much%20bigger%20movement%20to%20hold%20Starbucks%20accountable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20Starbucks%20location%20in%20Ithaca%20successfully%20voted%20to%20unionize%20last%20year%2C%20making%20it%20the%20first%20and%20only%20city%20to%20reach%20100%25%20Starbucks%20worker%20unionization.%20Starbucks%20executives%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-store-closure-in-new-york-retaliation-against-union-2022-6%5C%22%3Eshut%20down%3C%2Fa%3E%20one%20of%20those%20stores%20in%20June%20last%20year.%20Then%20it%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fone.starbucks.com%2Fget-the-facts%2Fclosing-ithaca-area-stores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclosed%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20remaining%20two%20in%20May.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnion%20organizers%20across%20these%20stores%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20were%20also%20Cornell%20students%2C%20said%20the%20closures%20constituted%20an%20act%20of%20union-busting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20S