and%20R%20N%20Laddha%20was%20hearing%20petitions%20filed%20by%20the%20officials%20and%20Jitender%20Kothari%2C%20who%20was%20appointed%20by%20the%20National%20Company%20Law%20Tribunal%20(NCLT)%20as%20an%20interim%20resolution%20professional%2C%20seeking%20for%20the%20FIR%20to%20be%20quashed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioners%20had%20sought%20interim%20order%20of%20protection%20from%20any%20coercive%20action%20and%20for%20the%20probe%20to%20be%20stayed%20in%20the%20case%20pending%20the%20hearing%20of%20their%20pleas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20after%20hearing%20brief%20arguments%20by%20senior%20counsel%20Desai%20said%20it%20would%20continue%20hearing%20the%20matter%20on%20Monday%20(August%2021).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmit%20Desai%20then%20sought%20the%20court%20to%20grant%20interim%20protection%20from%20any%20coercive%20action%20to%20the%20petitioners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%2C%20however%2C%20refused%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20will%20happen%20in%20two%20days%3F%20We%20have%20kept%20the%20matter%20on%20Monday%20for%20hearing.%26quot%3B%20Amit%20Desai%20submitted%20to%20the%20court%20that%20in%202016%2C%20Nitin%20Desai%20had%20taken%20a%20loan%20of%20Rs%20150%20crore%20from%20Edelweiss'%20company%20ECLF%20for%20general%20corporate%20purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPart%20of%20the%20money%20was%20used%20to%20pay%20earlier%20loans.%20The%20deceased%20(Desai)%20and%20his%20company%20used%20to%20take%20loans%20earlier%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20counsel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20in%202018%2C%20an%20additional%20loan%20of%20Rs%2038%20crore%20was%20sought%20of%20which%20Rs%2031%20crore%20was%20sanctioned%20and%20disbursed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmit%20Desai%20claimed%20that%20from%20the%20end%20of%202018%2C%20the%20art%20director%20started%20delaying%20the%20repayment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20then%20sought%20to%20know%20if%20the%202016%20loan%20was%20repaid%20before%20the%20additional%20loan%20amount%20was%20disbursed%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBetween%202016%20and%202018%20was%20the%20repayment%20timely%3F%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Sambre%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20senior%20counsel%20said%20between%202016%20and%202018%2C%20the%20repayment%20was%20done%20on%20schedule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20the%20end%20of%202018%2C%20there%20was%20a%20delay%20in%20the%20repayment%20schedule.%20Let%20me%20not%20call%20it%20default.%20There%20were%20delays%2C%26quot%3B%20Amit%20Desai%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20earlier%20judgments%20passed%20by%20the%20high%20court%20while%20quashing%20abetment%20of%20suicide%20cases%2C%20Amit%20Desai%20said%20abetment%20involves%20constant%20instigation%20and%20mens%20rea%20which%20are%20absent%20in%20the%20present%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20have%20to%20protect%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20financial%20capital%20of%20the%20country%20then%20the%20use%20of%20criminal%20action%20should%20also%20be%20such%20that%20we%20don't%20lose%20the%20standing%20of%20being%20the%20financial%20capital%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitin%20Desai%20(57)%2C%20who%20had%20worked%20for%20acclaimed%20Bollywood%20films%20like%20%26quot%3BLagaan%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BJodhaa%20Akbar%26quot%3B%2C%20was%20found%20hanging%20at%20his%20studio%20at%20Karjat%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Raigad%20district%20on%20August%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%204%2C%20his%20wife%20approached%20the%20Khalapur%20police%20station%20to%20register%20an%20FIR%20into%20his%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20this%2C%20an%20abetment%20of%20suicide%20case%20was%20registered%20against%20Shah%2C%20Bansal%2C%20Kothari%20and%20two%20others.%20The%20FIR%20was%20also%20registered%20against%20Kothari%20and%20two%20others%20under%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20sections%20306%20(abetment%20of%20suicide)%20and%2034%20(common%20intention).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitin%20Desai's%20company%20ND's%20Art%20World%20Pvt%20Ltd%20had%20defaulted%20on%20a%20Rs%20252%20crore%20loan%20repayment%20to%20creditors%20and%20the%20Mumbai%20bench%20of%20the%20NCLT%20had%20initiated%20insolvency%20proceedings%20against%20it.%20Edelweiss%20ARC%2C%20in%20a%20statement%20issued%20at%20the%20time%2C%20had%20denied%20that%20any%20undue%20pressure%20was%20put%20on%20the%20art%20director%20for%20loan%20recovery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Raigad%20police%2C%20who%20are%20probing%20into%20Desai's%20death%2C%20have%20found%2011%20audio%20clips%20in%20a%20voice%20recorder%20at%20the%20art%20director's%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20of%20the%20voice%20notes%20found%20after%20his%20alleged%20suicide%2C%20Desai%20criticised%20a%20financial%20services%20firm%20to%20which%20his%20company%20owed%20money%2C%20the%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDesai%20also%20purportedly%20said%20he%20had%20walked%20a%20long%20road%2C%20and%20could%20not%20go%20any%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20of%20these%20clips%20or%20voice%20notes%2C%20he%20was%20heard%20saying%20his%20company%20could%20not%20come%20out%20of%20the%20financial%20crisis%20it%20was%20facing%20because%20of%20the%20procedure%20adopted%20by%20the%20financial%20services%20firm%2C%20the%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitin%20Desai's%20death%20was%20also%20discussed%20in%20the%20Maharashtra%20assembly%2C%20where%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20said%20a%20probe%20would%20inquire%20into%20the%20%26quot%3Brole%20of%20creditors%20and%20whether%20he%20(was%20under%20mental%20stress%20and%20being%20pressured%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692364440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fnqr0e0fg_nitin-desai-ani_625x300_03_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fart-director-n