%20that%20copyright%20laws%20largely%20do%20not%20protect%20fashion%20once%20a%20product%20leaves%20the%20design%20stages%20and%20becomes%20a%20garment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20the%20company%20works%20with%20its%20manufacturers%20has%20also%20become%20a%20source%20of%20contention.%20Multiple%20investigations%20into%20factories%20that%20supply%20to%20Shein%20have%20found%20that%20the%20factories%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstories.publiceye.ch%2Fen%2Fshein%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eviolated%20labor%20rights%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20kept%20up%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sixthtone.com%2Fnews%2F1008472%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epoor%20working%20conditions%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20Insider%20after%20the%20interview%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20Shein%20said%20the%20company%20is%20committed%20to%20respecting%20human%20rights%20and%20adhering%20to%20local%20laws%20and%20regulations.%20Its%20suppliers%20must%20adhere%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bstrict%20code%20of%20conduct%26quot%3B%20that%20is%20aligned%20to%20the%20International%20Labour%20Organization's%20core%20conventions%2C%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223543%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Accounts%20accused%20of%20impersonating%20the%20Shein%20brand%20have%20been%20suspended.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64aa26d48ed31300199e3539%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222362%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EShein's%20use%20of%20audience-engagement%20technology%20and%20keeping%20on%20top%20of%20trends%20has%20helped%20it%20produce%20garments%20with%20exceptional%20speed.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Shein%20gathers%20data%20from%20shoppers%20online%20to%20identify%20trends%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EShein%20uses%20audience-engagement%20technology%20on%20its%20site%20and%20mobile%20app%20to%20identify%20trends%20and%20determine%20demand%2C%20Pernot-Day%20told%20Insider.%20Just%20as%20TikTok%20or%20Instagram%20tracks%20what%20you%20search%20or%20how%20long%20you%20engage%20with%20a%20particular%20video%2C%20Shein%20gathers%20similar%20data%20from%20its%20shoppers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20open%20Shein's%20app%2C%20that's%20one%20data%20point.%20If%20you%20visit%20Shein's%20website%20from%20an%20outside%20link%2C%20that%20referring%20page%20is%20a%20data%20point.%20This%20is%20a%20common%20practice%20in%20retail%20%E2%80%94%20many%20other%20brands%20track%20similar%20data%20on%20their%20sites.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20opening%20Shein's%20app%20or%20visiting%20the%20website%2C%20you%20begin%20what%20Pernot-Day%20called%20a%20%26quot%3Bsession%20journey%2C%26quot%3B%20where%20every%20click%20becomes%20valuable%20data%2C%20from%20the%20key%20words%20you%20type%20into%20the%20search%20bar%20to%20how%20you%20respond%20when%20the%20site%20shows%20you%20similar%20items%20to%20what%20you've%20been%20looking%20at.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20log%20into%20your%20account%20on%20Shein%2C%20you%20might%20find%20an%20experience%20similar%20to%20Netflix's%2C%20wherein%20you%20get%20personalized%20suggestions%20for%20the%20types%20of%20clothing%20you%20typically%20shop%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20of%20these%20customer%20journeys%2C%20each%20one%20can%20be%20very%20unique%20or%20aggregated%20and%20anonymized%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20measure%20demand%2C%20Shein's%20site%20then%20conducts%20statistical%20sampling%20to%20understand%20what%20sequence%20of%20steps%20led%20a%20customer%20to%20any%20given%20purchase.%20Once%20that%20sequence%20has%20occurred%20several%20times%2C%20the%20system%20projects%20a%20level%20of%20demand%20for%20a%20particular%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20Shein%20also%20gathers%20data%20through%20advertising%2C%20as%20many%20other%20retailers%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223828%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20model%20walks%20the%20runway%20during%20a%20Shein%20fashion%20show.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F649b6d0bec2dd400195fb648%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225741%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EShein%20gathers%20customer%20data%20from%20trends%20on%20its%20app%20and%20website%2C%20then%20uses%20that%20data%20throughout%20its%20supply%20chain.%3Cp%3EKristy%20Sparow%2FGetty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20'secret%20sauce'%20behind%20Shein's%20on-demand%20fashion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20technology%20Shein%20uses%20to%20determine%20trends%20isn't%20new%20%E2%80%94%20many%20online%20retailers%20collect%20similar%20data%20to%20track%20customer%20behaviors.%20But%20what%20Pernot-Day%20said%20makes%20Shein's%20business%20model%20different%20is%20how%20it%20uses%20this%20digital%20model%20throughout%20its%20supply%20chain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20Shein%20determines%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20product%2C%20it%20sends%20the%20projection%20to%20suppliers%20using%20a%20model%20it%20calls%20%26quot%3Bon-demand.%26quot%3B%20Shein%20produces%20a%20limited%20run%20of%20a%20product%20%E2%80%94%20typically%20only%20100%20to%20200%20units%20of%20that%20product.%20If%20that%20product%20performs%20well%2C%20Shein%20will%20place%20a%20bid%20with%20its%20manufacturers%20for%20a%20larger%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShein's%20manufacturers%20have%20access%20to%20a%20supplier-management%20system%20where%20they%20can%20monitor%20demand%20and%20see%20what's%20coming%20down%20the%20pipeline%2C%20Pernot-Day%20said.%20In%20turn%2C%20he%20said%2C%20manufacturers%20are%20willing%20to%20accept%20the%20small%20orders%20because%20they%20can%20see%20what's%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20really%20a%20marriage%20of%20audience-engagement%20technologies%2C%20which%20were%20developed%20in%20the%20early%202000s%2C%20with%20a%20di