%20with%20the%20student%20wing%20of%20Hindu%20nationalist%20outfit%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20before%20going%20on%20to%20contest%20two%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20against%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20Varanasi%20%E2%80%93%20was%20nominated%20by%20the%20Congress%20as%20its%20state%20president%20in%20politically-significant%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20on%20Thursday%2C%20August%2017.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERai%20is%20a%20former%20five-time%20MLA%20from%20Varanasi.%20He%20replaced%20Brij%20Lal%20Khabri%2C%20who%20had%20been%20appointed%20as%20the%20Congress%20state%20head%20less%20than%20a%20year%20ago%20in%20what%20was%20then%20seen%20as%20a%20move%20by%20the%20party%20to%20reignite%20interest%20among%20the%20numerically-important%20Dalit%20voters%20accounting%20for%2021.5%25%20of%20the%20state%20population.%20While%20Khabri%20is%20a%20Dalit%2C%20Rai%2C%2054%2C%20belongs%20to%20the%20dominant%20upper%20caste%20Bhumihar%20community%2C%20which%20though%20inconsequential%20in%20the%20overall%20caste%20arithmetic%20of%20UP%2C%20has%20political%20weight%20in%20districts%20around%20Varanasi%20and%20a%20strong%20sense%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98jati%20asmita%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%20or%20caste%20pride.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20a%20Congress%20source%20said%20that%20Rai%20seems%20to%20have%20been%20nominated%20to%20the%20post%20due%20to%20his%20personal%20record%20and%20influence%2C%20rather%20than%20just%20caste%20calculations.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20already%20have%20a%20Dalit%20(Mallikarjun%20Kharge)%20as%20the%20national%20president.%20In%20UP%20we%20want%20someone%20who%20can%20fight%20on%20the%20streets.%20We%20have%20picked%20someone%20who%20fought%20directly%20against%20Modi.%20We%20want%20to%20indicate%20that%20our%20fight%20is%20directly%20against%20the%20BJP%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20Congress%20source.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELike%20Khabri%2C%20Rai%20was%20also%20an%20import%20into%20the%20Congress.%20Khabri%20was%20a%20former%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%20MP%20from%20Jalaun.%20Rai%20had%20a%20long%20past%20with%20the%20BJP%20before%20he%20joined%20the%20Congress.%20He%20was%20last%20year%20appointed%20a%20provincial%20president%20of%20the%20party%20in%20East%20UP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20graduate%20of%20the%20Kashi%20Vidyapeeth%20in%20Varanasi%2C%20Rai%20began%20his%20career%20as%20a%20convenor%20of%20the%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Vidyarthi%20Parishad%20(ABVP)%2C%20the%20student%20wing%20of%20the%20RSS-BJP%2C%20in%201991-92.%20Rai%20participated%20in%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20movement%20and%20was%20even%20held%20in%20the%20Varanasi%20district%20jail%20under%20preventive%20sections%20of%20the%20law.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20entered%20electoral%20politics%20with%20a%20bang%20in%201996%20when%20he%20defeated%20nine-time%20sitting%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%20MLA%20Udal%20from%20the%20Kolasla%20seat.%20In%202002%2C%20he%20won%20from%20the%20Kolasla%20assembly%20constituency%20again.%20A%20few%20months%20later%20he%20was%20rewarded%20with%20a%20ministerial%20berth%20as%20state%20minister%20for%20cooperatives%20in%20the%20Mayawati-led%20BSP-BJP%20alliance%20government.%20After%20a%20third%20assembly%20win%20in%202007%2C%20feeling%20betrayed%20that%20the%20party%20had%20picked%20veteran%20leader%20Murli%20Manohar%20Joshi%20as%20its%20Lok%20Sabha%20candidate%20from%20Varanasi%20despite%20promising%20it%20to%20him%2C%20he%20quit%20the%20BJP%20in%202009.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20promised%20the%20ticket%20and%20I%20worked%20hard%20for%20a%20year.%20But%20for%20reasons%20unknown%20I%20was%20shunted%20at%20the%20last%20moment%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20me%20in%202014.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERai%20contested%20the%202009%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20as%20a%20candidate%20of%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party.%20He%20stood%20third%20with%201.23%20lakh%20votes%20but%20the%20contest%20would%20be%20remembered%20more%20for%20the%20way%20tainted%20politician%20and%20rival%20Bahubali%20of%20Purvanchal%20Mukhtar%20Ansari%20gave%20Joshi%20a%20run%20for%20his%20money.%20Ansari%20lost%20to%20Joshi%20by%20a%20relatively%20thin%20margin%20of%2017%2C000%20votes%20in%20what%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20communally%20polarised%20contest.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20though%20Rai%20denies%20it%2C%20in%20the%20narrow%20lanes%20and%20by-lanes%20of%20Varanasi%2C%20it%20is%20often%20said%20that%20after%20sensing%20that%20he%20would%20not%20win%2C%20Rai%20campaigned%20for%20Joshi%20to%20ensure%20Mukhtar%20Ansari%E2%80%99s%20defeat%20because%20of%20their%20bitter%20relationship.%20In%20June%202023%2C%20a%20Varanasi%20court%20convicted%20Ansari%20and%20sentenced%20him%20to%20life%20for%20murdering%20Rai%E2%80%99s%20brother%20Awadesh%20Rai%20in%201991.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERai%E2%80%99s%20journey%20with%20the%20Congress%20started%20in%202012%20when%20he%20contested%20as%20its%20candidate%20and%20routed%20the%20BJP%20nominee%20to%20secure%20Pindra%20(earlier%20known%20as%20Kolasla).%20The%20BJP%20candidate%20was%20reduced%20to%203%2C000%20votes%20as%20Rai%20got%20his%20sweet%20revenge.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20in%20this%20setting%20that%20the%20Congress%20in%202014%2C%20looking%20to%20prevent%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20prime%20ministerial%20face%20Narendra%20Modi%20from%20securing%20Varanasi%2C%20one%20of%20the%20holiest%20Hindu%20cities%2C%20picked%20Rai%20as%20his%20challenger.%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20was%20the%20other%20candidate%20in%20the%20highly-watched%20contest.%20Rai%E2%80%99s%20nomination%20elevated%20his%20stature.%20However%2C%20since%20the%20contest%20was%20reduced%20to%20a%20fight%20between%20Modi%20and%20Kejriwal%2C%20he%20had%20to%20contend%20with%20a%20third-place%20finish.%20The%20same%20thing%20happened%20in%202019%20when%20the%20SP-BSP%20alliance%20candidate%20o%20edg