0batting%20coach%20backed%20Kohli%20and%20stated%20that%20the%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bangalore%20star%20should%20definitely%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Indian%20team%20in%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B100%20percent.%20Just%20look%20at%20what%20he%20did%20in%20the%20previous%20World%20Cup.%20Those%20close%20matches%20-%20there%20were%20some%20edge-of-the-seat%20encounters%20where%20emotions%20run%20high%20and%20you%20know%20that%20this%20is%20a%20big-stage%20game%20where%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20national%20are%20glued%20on%20you.%20One%20small%20mistake%20can%20make%20a%20difference.%20That's%20where%20you%20need%20players%20who%20have%20gone%20through%20those%20situations.%20At%20that%20point%2C%20it%20doesn't%20really%20matter%20what%20your%20strike-rate%20is%20or%20how%20you've%20done%20in%20the%20IPL.%20No%2C%20in%20a%20big%20game%2C%20you%20require%20big%20match%20players%20and%20he%20showed%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Flive%2FXcOKpXTbnqQ%3Ffeature%3Dshare%5C%22%3EBangar%20said%20on%20Cricket%20Basu%20YouTube%20channel.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20RCB%20head%20coach%20further%20gave%20a%20reference%20of%20Virat's%20IPL%202023%20century%20against%20Gujarat%20Titans%2C%20where%20he%20smashed%20101%20runs%20off%20just%2061%20balls%2C%20laced%20with%2013%20fours%20and%20only%20one%20six.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRecall%20the%20India%20vs%20Pakistan%20game.%20Even%20for%20that%20matter%2C%20the%20quarterfinal%20between%20India%20and%20Australia%20in%20the%202016%20T20%20World%20Cup.%20He%20has%20been%20doing%20it%20consistently.%20Everyone%20has%20their%20own%20style%20of%20making%20runs%2C%20and%20it's%20not%20mandatory%20to%20have%20six-hitters%20to%20win%20matches.%20Had%20it%20been%20the%20case%2C%20West%20Indies%20would%20have%20won%20all%20T20%20World%20Cups.%20Kohli%20is%20a%20player%20who%20can%20smash%20a%20100%20without%20even%20hitting%20a%20six.%20If%20you%20don't%20have%20players%20who%20can%20soak%20in%20pressure%2C%20then%20you%20are%20asking%20for%20trouble%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20Team%20India%20is%20all%20set%20to%20square%20off%20against%20Ireland%20in%20the%20three-match%20T20I%20series%2C%20under%20the%20captaincy%20of%20their%20star%20pacer%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Jasprit%20Bumrah%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1724-jasprit-bumrah-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJasprit%20Bumrah%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20series%20will%20kick-start%20on%20Friday%20in%20Dublin.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692360480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2Fuii2bi28_virat-kohli-afp_625x300_10_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fwhy-india-need-virat-kohli-in-2024-t20-world-cup-ex-india-star-explains-4304874%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Virat%20Kohli%20is%20undoubtedly%20one%20of%20the%20greatest%20batters%20in%20the%20world%20across%20all%20three%20formats.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fwhy-india-need-virat-kohli-in-2024-t20-world-cup-ex-india-star-explains-4304874%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fwhy-india-need-virat-kohli-in-2024-t20-world-cup-ex-india-star-explains-4304874%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fwhy-india-need-virat-kohli-in-2024-t20-world-cup-ex-india-star-explains-4304874%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rahul%20Gandhi%20To%20Contest%20From%20Amethi%20In%202024%3A%20UP%20Congress%20Chief%20Ajay%20Rai%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECongress%20MP%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20will%20contest%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20from%20Amethi%2C%20the%20party's%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20chief%20Ajay%20Rai%20said%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRahul%20Gandhi%20will%20contest%20from%20Amethi%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%26quot%3B%20Ajay%20Rai%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20speculations%20that%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20will%20contest%20the%202024%20elections%2C%20Mr%20Rai%20said%20that%20she%20will%20contest%20from%20wherever%20she%20wants%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20wishes%20to%20contest%20from%20Varanasi%2C%20every%20worker%20will%20strive%20to%20make%20her%20win%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20appointed%20Ajay%20Rai%20as%20the%20chief%20of%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Congress%20Committee%20with%20immediate%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCongress%20president%20has%20appointed%20Ajay%20Rai%2C%20ex-MLA%20as%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Congress%20Committee%20with%20immediate%20effect%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20release%20of%20All%20India%20Congress%20Committee%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjay%20Rai%20was%20the%20Congress%20candidate%20from%20Varanasi%20in%202014%20and%202019.%20He%20lost%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20both%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20businessman%20Robert%20Vadra%20strongly%20pitched%20for%20his%20wife%20and%20Congress%20leader%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20to%20fight%20the%202024%20general%20elections%2C%20saying%20people%20will%20feel%20good%20if%20she%20comes%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20the%20party%20could%20field%20her%20from%20Amethi%20or%20Sultanpur%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20I%20feel%20Priyanka%20should%20reach%20the%20parliament%20first%20and%20people%20will%20feel%20good%20if%20she%20comes%20to%20Lok%20Sabha.%20Be%20it%20Amethi%20or%20Sultanpur%2C%20wherever%20the%20party%20seems%20fit%2C%20I%20would%20like%20her%20to%20contest%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Vadra%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692360240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F023amhm8_rahul-gandhi_625x300_13_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2024-lok-sabha-elections-rahul-gandhi-to-contest-from-amethi-says-up-congress-chief-ajay-rai-4308876%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress%20MP%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20will%20contest%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20from%20Amethi%2C%20the%20party's%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20chief%20Ajay%20Rai%20said%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2024-lok-sabha-elections-rahul-gandhi-to-contest-from-amethi-says-up-congress-chief-ajay-rai-4308876%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2024-lok-sabha-elections-rahul-gandhi-to-contest-from-amethi-says-up-congress-chief-ajay-rai-4308876%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2024-lok-sabha-elections-rahul-gandhi-to-contest-from-amethi-says-up-congress-chief-ajay-rai-4308876%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCan't%20Have%20Frugal%20Engineering%20Alone%2C%20Need%20Bigger%20Rockets%26quot%3B%3A%20Ex-ISRO%20Chief%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia's%20Mars%20mission%20may%20have%20cost%20less%20than%20some%20Hollywood%20films%2C%20but%20the%20era%20of%20%3Cem%3Ejugaad%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20frugal%20engineering%20in%20the%20country%20will%20need%20to%20make%20way%20for%20more%20money%20and%20bigger%20rockets%20in%20the%20future%2C%20former%20ISRO%20chief%20K%20Sivan%20has%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Chandrayaan-3%20launched%20on%20July%2014%20and%20the%20lander%20is%20expected%20to%20touch%20down%20on%20the%20Moon%20on%20August%2023%2C%20Russia%20launched%20its%20lunar%20mission%20on%20August%2010%20and%20a%20landing%20is%20planned%20on%20August%2021.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20huge%20difference%20in%20the%20time%20taken%20by%20the%20missions%20is%20because%20India%20opted%20to%20slingshot%20to%20the%20Moon%2C%20which%20involves%20using%20the%20Earth's%20gravity%20to%20propel%20a%20spacecraft%20on%20its%20trajectory%2C%20while%20Russia%20used%20a%20heavier%20rocket%20to%20place%20the%20satellite%20directly%20into%20the%20lunar%20orbit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20NDTV%20today%2C%20Mr%20Sivan%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20bigger%20rockets%20and%20bigger%20systems.%20We%20cannot%20live%20with%20frugal%20engineering%20alone.%20We%20need%20to%20have%20high-power%20rockets%20and%20high-end%20technology.%20For%20that%2C%20this%20government%20has%20done%20one%20good%20thing%3A%20they%20have%20opened%20up%20space%20activities%20to%20private%20industries.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20ISRO%20chief%20said%20the%20private%20sector%20is%20showing%20interest%20and%20the%20results%20have%20already%20started%20showing.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20sure%20they%20will%20soon%20be%20able%20to%20take%20up%20high-end%20technology%20as%20well.%20Investment%20won't%20be%20a%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20India's%20ambitions%20will%20get%20a%20boost%20with%20the%20Gaganyaan%20mission%2C%20which%20will%20be%20the%20country's%20first%20manned%20mission%20in%20space.%20%26quot%3BOnce%20this%20technology%20is%20proven%20and%20available%2C%20we%20can%20think%20of%20a%20space%20station%2C%20a%20permanent%20human%20habitat%20on%20the%20Moon%20and%20many%20other%20things.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECasting%20light%20on%20the%20reaction%20of%20scientists%20to%20Chandrayaan-1%20finding%20water%20on%20the%20Moon%20in%202009.%20%C2%A0Mr%20Sivan%20said%20it%20was%20a%20really%20exciting%20moment%20for%20the%20entire%20Isro%20community.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20something%20was%20told%20that%20it%20is%20not%20there%20and%20we%20discovered%20it%20(sic).%20I%20also%20rejoiced%20at%20the%20discovery.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20importance%20of%20rockets%20and%20ISRO's%20evolution%20from%20using%20the%20Polar%20Satellite%20Launch%20Vehicle%20(PSLV)%2C%20then%20the%20Geosynchronous%20Satellite%20Launch%20Vehicle%20(GSLV)%20and%20now%20the%20Launch%20Vehicle%20Mark-III%20(LVM3)%2C%20Mr%20Sivan%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFor%20space%20systems%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20a%20rocket%20or%20spacecraft%20or%20anything%20else%2C%20how%20they%20differ%20from%20terrestrial%20systems%20is%20in%20terms%20of%20quality%20and%20reliability.%20Without%20these%2C%20we%20would%20not%20achieve%20any%20of%20the%20missions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSpace%20systems%20will%20get%20a%20chance%20to%20work%20only%20once%2C%20and%20that%20too%20in%20space.%20So%20our%20systems%20have%20been%20built%20perfectly%20to%20the%20level%20of%20quality%20and%20reliability%20that%20we%20expected%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20significance%20of%20India%20developing%20cryogenic%20engines%20despite%20pressure%20from%20the%20West%2C%20the%20former%20ISRO%20chief%20said%20the%20engines%20are%20essential%20to%20enhance%20payload%20capabilities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithout%20that%2C%20the%20mass%20of%20the%20satellites%20that%20we%20can%20carry%20would%20be%20reduced.%20We%20started%20developing%20cryogenic%20engines%20on%20our%20own.%20Initially%2C%20we%20worked%20with%20Russians%20to%20produce%20engines%20of%20a%20similar%20kind.%20We%20have%20now%20developed%20new%2C%20high-power%20cryogenic%20engines%20that%20are%20working%20very%20well.%20Now%2C%20we%20are%20working%20on%20semi-cryogenic%20engine%20technology%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20India%20is%20working%20on%20reusable%20rockets%2C%20like%20SpaceX%20is%20doing%2C%20the%20former%20ISRO%20chief%20said%20technology%20demonstrations%20are%20being%20conducted%20for%20vertical%20landing%20and%20such%20rockets%20can%20be%20developed%20once%20that%20is%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sivan%20said%20ISRO%20gives%20equal%20opportunities%20to%20men%20and%20women%2C%20and%20urged%20young%20Indians%20to%20develop%20a%20scientific%20temper%20so%20that%20they%20can%20help%20the%20country%20in%20the%20future%20with%20their%20discoveries.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692360180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Frotit2lc_chandrayaan-3-launch_625x300_14_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcant-have-frugal-engineering-alone-need-bigger-rockets-ex-isro-chief-4308976%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20Mars%20mission%20may%20have%20cost%20less%20than%20some%20Hollywood%20films%2C%20but%20the%20era%20of%20jugaad%20and%20frugal%20engineering%20in%20the%20country%20will%20need%20to%20make%20way%20for%20more%20money%20and%20bigger%20rockets%20in%20the%20future%2C%20former%20ISRO%20chief%20K%20Sivan%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcant-have-frugal-engineering-alone-need-bigger-rockets-ex-isro-chief-4308976%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcant-have-frugal-engineering-alone-need-bigger-rockets-ex-isro-chief-4308976%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcant-have-frugal-engineering-alone-need-bigger-rockets-ex-isro-chief-4308976%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dhillon%20and%20rumoured%20gf%20Banita's%20sweet%20banter%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692360122000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102835291%2Cimgsize-64060.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fhindi%2Fap-dhillon-is-nervous-as-his-docuseries-drops-on-ott-rumoured-girlfriend-banita-sandhu-has-the-sweetest-wish-for-him%2Farticleshow%2F102835359.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%