edly%20opened%20fire%20and%20struck%20the%20singer%20and%20the%20woman.%20Ms%20Tenorio%20was%20declared%20dead%20at%20the%20scene%20whereas%20the%20singer%20was%20taken%20to%20a%20clinic%20and%20then%20rushed%20to%20a%20hospital.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndependent%20%3C%2Fem%3Ereport%2C%20Mr%20Fortunato%20was%20on%20medical%20leave%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cop%20testified%20on%20August%2015%20and%20was%20released%20after%20two%20hours%20of%20questioning.%20An%20investigation%20is%20still%20ongoing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENelson%20Souza%20Filho%2C%20the%20uncle%20of%20MC%20Serginho%20Porradao%2C%20told%20Independent%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20simply%20in%20the%20wrong%20place%20at%20the%20wrong%20time.%20Everything%20he%20did%20for%20his%20family%20and%20the%20community%20was%20good.%26quot%3B%20Furthermore%2C%20he%20said%20that%20the%20victim's%20aunt%20had%20asked%20him%20not%20to%20perform%20at%20the%20concert%2C%20but%20he%20insisted%20and%20told%20them%20that%20he%20would%20%26quot%3Bcome%20back%20quickly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMay%20justice%20be%20done%2C%20both%20by%20the%20police%20and%20God%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFelipe%20Goncalves%2C%20brother%20of%20the%20singer%2C%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20extremely%20saddened%20by%20this%20tragedy.%20Serginho%20was%20always%20enjoying%20life%20and%20joking%20around.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20was%20a%20wonderful%20person%20who%20gave%20good%20vibes%20everywhere%20he%20went.%20He%20will%20be%20greatly%20missed%2C%26quot%3B%20Oziel%20Ferreira%2C%20MC%20Serginho%20Porradao's%20old%20friend%2C%20said%20in%20a%20tribute.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692359220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fdrtr4jhg_brazil-singer_625x300_18_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbrazilian-singer-shot-dead-while-performing-at-concert-4308929