ngly.%20Interdisciplinary%20PG%20programmes%20that%20consistently%20received%20over%20400%20applications%20now%20receive%20a%20few%20dozen%20applications.%20Even%20the%20most%20popular%20programmes%20have%20seen%20reduced%20numbers%20of%20applicants.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20added%20that%20externally%20funded%20projects%20have%20dried%20up.%20%E2%80%9CAUD%20faculty%20and%20Centres%20regularly%20undertook%20projects%20and%20consultancies%20worth%20around%20Rs%205-7%20crores%20a%20year.%20This%20number%20barely%20reaches%20Rs%201%20crore%20today.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%202020%2C%20more%20than%2015%20faculty%20members%2C%20including%20seasoned%20academics%2C%20have%20resigned%20from%20the%20university.%20Some%20have%20transitioned%20to%20private%20institutions%2C%20while%20others%20have%20departed%20from%20AUD%20without%20securing%20new%20positions%20due%20to%20the%20existing%20challenging%20work%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFaculty%20members%20regularly%20face%20obstacles%20such%20as%20denied%20NOCs%20(no-objection%20certificates)%20for%20academic%20engagements%2C%20visa%20issues%2C%20and%20delayed%20approvals%20for%20academic%20positions.%20Cumbersome%20procedures%20for%20external%20projects%20are%20causing%20some%20faculty%20to%20abandon%20research%20opportunities%20to%20avoid%20red%20tape%20in%20applying%20for%20and%20carrying%20out%20external%20grants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20further%20noted%20that%20the%20posts%20of%20visiting%20faculty%20on%20contract%20(in%20lieu%20of%20regular%20faculty)%20have%20been%20disbanded%20in%20favour%20of%20guest%20faculty%2C%20leading%20to%20poorer%20remuneration%20for%20the%20concerned%20faculty%20and%20gaps%20in%20faculty%20support%20for%20programmes%20to%20run%20optimally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFaculty%20is%20harassed%20by%20the%20administration%20on%20different%20grounds.%20There%20is%20a%20running%20thread%20of%20purposeful%20regressive%20reinterpretation%20of%20decisions%20taken%