20ODI%20World%20Cup%2C%20Akhtar%20doesn't%20feel%20Kohli%20should%20play%20white-ball%20cricket%20anymore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReliving%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%202022%20showdown%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20in%20Melbourne%2C%20Akhtar%20said%20that%20the%20match%20gave%20Kohli%20back%20his%20'kingdom'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20match%20was%20all%20about%20Virat%20Kohli.%20The%20cricket%20Gods%20wanted%20to%20do%20it%20for%20him.%20He%20wasn't%20in%20the%20best%20of%20form%2C%20and%20was%20facing%20a%20lot%20of%20heat%20from%20you%20guys%20in%20India.%20The%20media%20was%20after%20him.%20It%20was%20God's%20way%20of%20telling%20him%20-%20this%20is%20your%20stage%2C%20come%20and%20become%20king%20again.%20If%20you%20see%20all%20that%20transpired%20-%20rain%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20it%2C%20100%2C000%20people%2C%201.3%20billion%20Indians%20watching%2C%2030%20crore%20Pakistanis%20watching%2C%20the%20whole%20world%20in%20awe%20-%20the%20stage%20was%20set%20for%20Kohli.%20It%20was%20the%20greatest%20stage%20of%20all.%20When%20you%20add%20the%20two%20sixes%20he%20hit%20off%20Haris%20Rauf%2C%20that%20match%20gave%20him%20back%20his%20kingdom.%20I%20think%20it%20was%20all%20destined%20for%20him%20on%20that%20day%20at%20the%20MCG%2C%26quot%3B%20Akhtar%20said%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frevsportz.in%2Fshoaib-akhtar-exclusive-india-pakistan-matches-not-for-the-faint-hearted-shoaib-akhtar%2F%5C%22%3EBackstage%20With%20Boria%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20on%20Kohli%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20he%20should%20play%20more%2050-overs%20matches%20after%20this%20World%20Cup.%20Also%2C%20if%20you%20see%20him%20in%20T20s%2C%20it%20takes%20a%20lot%20out%20of%20him.%20I%20think%20he%20should%20play%20for%20at%20least%20six%20more%20years%20and%20break%20the%20100%20hundreds%20record%20of%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sachin%20Tendulkar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F14-sachin-tendulkar-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESach