20precipitation%20could%20also%20impact%20standing%20rice%20crops%2C%20which%20will%20be%20harvested%20in%20October.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20states%2C%20including%20Bihar%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Odisha%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20are%20set%20to%20be%20lashed%20by%20heavy%20rains%20in%20the%20coming%20days%2C%20according%20to%20the%20India%20Meteorological%20Department%2C%20or%20IMD.%20The%20risk%20of%20flash%20floods%20in%20some%20areas%20has%20also%20increased%2C%20it%20said%20on%20Friday.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHimachal%20Pradesh%20is%20bearing%20the%20brunt%20of%20extreme%20weather%2C%20with%20the%20death%20count%20rising%20to%20over%20330%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20monsoon.%20Some%20500%20people%2C%20who%20were%20stranded%20when%20a%20dam%20opened%20its%20gates%20on%20Monday%20night%20to%20avoid%20damage%20to%20its%20structure%2C%20were%20rescued%20by%20Air%20Force%20helicopters%20and%20other%20teams%20working%20in%20the%20area%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Home%20Ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Army%20and%20the%20National%20Disaster%20Response%20Force%20(NDRF)%20rescued%20about%20300%20people%20on%20Thursday%20from%20flood-hit%20villages%20of%20Punjab%2C%20news%20agency%20PTI%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParts%20of%20Delhi%20and%20Mumbai%20were%20also%20flooded%20last%20month%20due%20to%20heavy%20rains%20for%20several%20days.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692356160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Foo6p8o2g_himachal-rain_625x300_30_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frain-landslide-monsoon-fury-in-himachal-pradesh-uttarakhand-punjab-india-braces-for-more-rain-after-floods-lightning-kill-2-000-4308717%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Parts%20of%20India%20are%20bracing%20for%20more%20torrential%20rain%2C%20raising%20the%20risk%20of%20further%20causalities%20after%20natural%20calamities%20such%20as%20floods%20and%20lightning%20kill