20really%20bothers%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20this%20passion%20that%20led%20him%20to%20create%20the%20infamous%20viral%20video%20in%20April%20this%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20label%20on%20that%20drink%20says%20that%20you%20get%20stronger%20bones%20and%20muscles.%20The%20reason%20I%20chose%20to%20make%20a%20video%20on%20this%20drink%20is%20because%20people%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F301227%2Fharvard-law-mba-grad-empower-underprivileged-kids-to-eat-healthy-through-games-foodshaala-foundation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efeel%20this%20is%20healthy%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20have%20no%20qualms%20about%20giving%20this%20twice%20a%20day%20to%20their%20children%20%E2%80%94%20that%E2%80%99s%2014%20times%20a%20week.%20People%20think%20aerated%20drinks%20like%20coke%20are%20unhealthy%2C%20which%20we%20may%20have%20only%20once%20a%20week.%20But%20the%20former%20has%20a%20direct%20impact%20on%20our%20health%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20his%20Instagram%20%40foodpharmer%2C%20Revant%20educates%20about%20500%2C000%20of%20his%20followers%20on%20how%20they%20can%20make%20healthier%20choices.%20These%20include%20videos%20decoding%20labels%20of%20popular%20packaged%20noodles%2C%20drinks%2C%20biscuits%2C%20sauces%20and%20more%2C%20as%20well%20as%20helping%20people%20decide%20which%20bread%20is%20better%20for%20them%2C%20which%20drink%20they%20can%20choose%2C%20etc.%20He%20is%20also%20promoting%20small%20businesses%20that%20are%20%E2%80%9Crelatively%20healthier%E2%80%9D%20than%20the%20bigger%20brands.%20His%20goal%20is%20to%20help%20people%20choose%20better%2C%20he%20says.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERemember%20this%20next%20time%20you%E2%80%99re%20at%20the%20supermarket%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCwChJrSNO2I%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCwChJrSNO2I%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCwChJrSNO2I%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Revant%20Himatsingka%20(%40foodpharmer)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Revant%20agrees%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20possible%20to%20live%20without%20consuming%20packaged%20food%2C%20he%20just%20wants%20people%20to%20make%20informed%20choices.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F263656%2Fhealthy-diet-recipes-rujuta-diwekar-work-from-home-weight-loss-video-viral%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etwo%20types%20of%20junk%20food%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20one%20is%20junk%20food%20that%20pretends%20to%20be%20healthy%20food%2C%20and%20the%20second%20is%20just%20junk%20food.%20My%20problem%20is%20with%20the%20former%2C%20which%20I%20want%20to%20expose%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20emphasises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20how%20can%20we%20make%20good%20everyday%20choices%20when%20we%20pick%20our%20food%3F%20For%20this%2C%20Revant%20shares%20six%20tips%20with%20us%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EIngredients%20are%20listed%20in%20order%20of%20their%20weight%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20first%20ingredient%20is%20the%20one%20the%20packet%20contains%20the%20most.%20So%20if%20you%E2%80%99re%20buying%20biscuits%2C%20the%20first%20three%20ingredients%20usually%20will%20be%20maida%20(refined%20wheat%20flour)%2C%20palm%20oil%20and%20sugar%E2%80%9D%20says%20Revant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBuy%20items%20that%20have%20less%20than%20five%20ingredients%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTry%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20products%20that%20have%20more%20than%20five%20ingredients.%20As%20the%20ingredient%20list%20increases%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20inversely%20proportional%20to%20the%20nutritional%20benefits.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%223%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAvoid%20products%20that%20have%20complicated%20ingredients%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20recognise%20or%20pronounce%20ingredients%20in%20a%20product%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20good%20for%20you.%20Buy%20the%20product%20in%20which%20you%20can%20understand%20the%20ingredient%2C%20like%20something%20that%20says%20dates%2C%20peanuts%2C%20milk%2C%20etc.%20If%20something%20has%20ingredients%20like%20maltodextrin%2C%20anti-caking%20agent%2C%20technical%20chemicals%2C%20stay%20away%20from%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%224%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBuy%20items%20that%20don%E2%80%99t%20list%20sugar%20in%20the%20first%205-6%20ingredients%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSteer%20clear%20of%20products%20that%20have%20sugar%20listed%20first%20or%20second.%20Those%20products%20are%20basically%20just%20sugar.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%225%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EGo%20for%20the%20slightly%20healthier%20options%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20whole%20idea%20is%20to%20make%20healthier%20choices.%20Instead%20of%20going%20for%20a%20%3Cem%3Emaida%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebiscuit%2C%20go%20for%20an%20%3Cem%3Eatta%20%3C%2Fem%3E(whole%20wheat%20flour)%20biscuit.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%226%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20best%20food%20for%20you%20is%20one%20that%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20label%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUltimately%2C%20the%20healthiest%20foods%20are%20the%20ones%20without%20any%20labels%2C%20fruits%20and%20vegetables.%20If%20you%20must%20buy%20other%20products%2C%20go%20for%20simple%20products%20that%20have%20ingredients%20you%20know.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20you%E2%80%99re%20buying%20peanut%20butter%2C%20go%20for%20products%20which%20just%20have%20peanuts%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Revant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20quest%20to%20make%20the%20next%20generation%20healthier%20and%20wiser%20about%20their%20food%20choices%2C%20Revant%20dreams%20of%20a%20day%20when%20every%20child%20is%20taught%20how%20to%20read%20food%20labels.%20He%20now%20goes%20to%20schools%20and%20colleges%20to%20teach%20students%20this%20skill%20as%20well.%20Here%2C%20he%20often%20finds%20that%20children%20ask%20interesting%20and%20intelligent%20questions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20question%20why%20the%20front%20of%20the%20packets%20say%20something%20that%20the%20product%20clearly%20does%20not%20do.%20They%20want%20to%20know%20why%20their%20favourite%20celebrity%20is%20endorsing%20a%20product%20which%20is%20unhealthy.%20I%20am%20hopeful%20that%20this%20will%20lead%20to%20better%20choices%2C%E2%80%9D%20smiles%20Revant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20children%20are%20taught%20how%20to%20r