5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Flink.sbstck.com%2Fredirect%2F14c1635e-a7ae-4e9f-8b95-00620f837404%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1692412367802000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw2VXXfQT99vUvLdDUL9mpiq%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecaught%20on%20camera%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0approaching%20Xi%20at%20Bali%20during%20the%20G20%20summit%20dinner.%20The%20foreign%20secretary%20then%20claimed%20it%20was%20just%20a%20meet%20and%20greet%20moment%2C%20but%20in%20the%20readout%20of%20a%20recent%20meeting%20between%20Ajit%20Doval%20and%20Wang%20Yi%2C%20Beijing%20revealed%20that%20the%20two%20leaders%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flink.sbstck.com%2Fredirect%2F53c9bed1-545e-42c3-966b-a25319959abe%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Flink.sbstck.com%2Fredirect%2F53c9bed1-545e-42c3-966b-a25319959abe%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1692412367802000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw0659QpceQiOYmUXktIt7fS%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehad%20spoken%20of%20the%20need%20to%20stabilise%20ties%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20Modi%20government%20was%20then%20forced%20to%20acknowledge%20that%20it%20had%20skipped%20mentioning%20this%20in%20its%20answers%20to%20journalists%20during%20the%20press%20briefing%20after%20the%20Bali%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20meeting%20between%20Modi%20and%20Xi%20helps%20resolve%20the%20border%20crisis%2C%20there%20could%20be%20nothing%20better%20for%20India%20and%20the%20region.%20The%20operative%20word%20here%20is%20%E2%80%9Cresolve%E2%80%9D%2C%20because%20this%20is%20the%20most%20worrying%20part%20of%20the%20latest%20joint%20statement.%20Consider%20this%20bit%3A%20%E2%80%9Cdiscussion%20on%20the%20resolution%20of%20remaining%20issues%20along%20the%20LAC%20in%20the%20Western%20sector%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3Cem%3EIpso%20facto%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ethis%20implies%20that%20many%20issues%20have%20been%20resolved%20on%20the%20Ladakh%20border%20between%20the%20two%20sides%2C%20a%20phrasing%20that%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flink.sbstck.com%2Fredirect%2Fe611e5bd-5c26-47a2-80ca-651ad2c671e0%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Flink.sbstck.com%2Fredirect%2Fe611e5bd-5c26-47a2-80ca-651ad2c671e0%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1692412367802000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw05lQOHLx8lHtc4ShrxnIWc%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20been%20recently%20used%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20external%20affairs%20minister%20S.%20Jaishankar%20as%20well.%20These%20areas%20of%20Chinese%20ingress%2C%20or%20%E2%80%9Cfriction%20points%E2%80%9D%20as%20Jaishankar%20calls%20them%2C%20which%20stand%20resolved%20as%20per%20this%20description%20are%3A%20Galwan%2C%20Gogra%2C%20Kugrang%20valley%20(widely%20misreported%20as%20Hot%20Springs)%2C%20the%20north%20bank%20of%20Pangong%20lake%20and%20the%20Kailash%20range.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20has%20happened%20at%20these%20places%20is%20only%20disengagement%2C%20which%20means%20that%20soldiers%20from%20both%20armies%20who%20were%20deployed%20in%20an%20eyeball-to-eyeball%20confrontation%20have%20stepped%20back%20by%20a%20few%20kilometres.%20Separating%20them%20is%20a%20buffer%20zone%20or%20a%20not-patrol%20area%2C%20which%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20mostly%20in%20the%20areas%20Indian%20soldiers%20were%20patrolling%20till%20May%202020.%20This%20is%20nothing%20close%20to%20resolution%2C%20which%20means%20a%20return%20to%C2%A0%3Cem%3Estatus%20quo%20ante%20bellum%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20situation%20as%20it%20existed%20before%20the%20crisis%20began%20in%202020.%20That%20would%20mean%20de-escalation%2C%20where%20additional%20forces%20step%20back%20to%20their%20semi-permanent%20bases%20100-150%20km%20away%2C%20and%20finally%20de-induction%2C%20where%20additional%20troops%20that%20came%20into%20the%20Ladakh%20sector%20are%20sent%20back%20to%20their%20peacetime%20locations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chinese%20have%20publicly%20refused%20to%20accept%20any%20return%20to%C2%A0%3Cem%3Estatus%20quo%20ante%20bellum%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20there%20has%20been%20no%20worthwhile%20conversation%20in%20these%2019%20rounds%20about%20de-escalation%20and%20de-induction%20from%20Ladakh.%20Indian%20forces%20continue%20to%20be%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flink.sbstck.com%2Fredirect%2Fa8bfec63-5a7e-4b87-93cf-b3d2d6924bc9%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Flink.sbstck.com%2Fredirect%2Fa8bfec63-5a7e-4b87-93cf-b3d2d6924bc9%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1692412367802000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1N3xESq-6PjtrYo0H-yy1_%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edenied%20access%20to%2026%20of%20the%2065%20patrolling%20points%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0(many%20of%20them%20well%20inside%20the%20LAC%20on%20the%20Indian%20side)%2C%20including%20in%20the%20areas%20where%20disengagement%20has%20taken%20place.%20Disengagement%20is%20a%20welcome%20exercise%20as%20a%20military%20expedient%20to%20reduce%20the%20risk%20of%20escalation%20by%20separating%20the%20soldiers%20of%20two%20armies%2C%20but%20it%20is%20nowhere%20near%20resolution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20the%20Chinese%20would%20want%20to%20depict%20disengagement%20as%20resolution%20is%20understandable%20because%20it%20is%20to%20their%20advantage%2C%20but%20why%20the%20Modi%20government%20is%20agreeing%20to%20such%20a%20proposition%20is%20hard%20to%20grasp.%20After%20all%2C%20it%20has%20witnessed%20this%20play%20in%20Doklam%20in%202017.%20After%20Modi%20and%20Xi%20met%20in%20Germany%20during%20the%20Doklam%20crisis%2C%20the%20two%20sides%20announced%20disengagement%20%E2%80%93%20again%20portrayed%20as%20%E2%80%9Cresolution%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20Indian%20government%20%E2%80%93%20that%20allowed%20Modi%20to%20travel%20to%20China%20for%20the%20BRICS%20summit.%20A%20few%20months%20later%2C%20the%20government%20was%20forced%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flink.sbstck.com%2Fredirect%2F8f9d83d3-7b5d-425e-9f1c-38176fad01e5%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Flink.sbstck.com%2Fredirect%2F8f9d83d3-7b5d-425e-9f1c-38176fad01e5%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1692412367802000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw050sc3Z58eMVU7wyHFh79T%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eacknowledge%20in%20Parliament%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20the%20Chinese%20had%20stepped%20back%20by%20a%20few%20hundred%20metres%20and%20constructed%20massive%20military%20infrastructure%20in%20the%20area.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Indian%20soldiers%20had%20returned%20to%20their%20original%20deployment%20positions%20under%20the%20disengagement%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20one%20wants%20to%20see%20a%20repeat%20of%20the%20Doklam%20%E2%80%9Cresolution%E2%80%9D%20in%20Ladakh.%20Let%20there%20be%20no%20doubt%20that%20only%20a%20return%20to%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3Estatus%20quo%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eof%20May%202020%20means%20resolution.%20Disengagement%20certainly%20isn%E2%80%99t.%20The%20price%20for%20mistaking%20disengagement%20for%20resolution%20in%20Ladakh%20will%20be%20too%20heavy%20for%20India%20to%20afford.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20piece%20was%20first%20published%20on%20The%20India%20Cable%20%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%20The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%20click%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692352846000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2Fsatellite-map-of-doklam-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fon-the-india-china-border-disengagement-is-not-resolution%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Only%20a%20return%20to%20the%C2%A0status%20quo%C2%A0of%20May%202020%20means%20resolution.%20Disengagement%20certainly%20isn%E2%80%99t.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fon-the-india-china-border-disengagement-is-not-resolution%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russia%20charges%20jailed%20US%20citizen%20with%20espionage%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692352780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102832048%2Cimgsize-17984.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussia-charges-jailed-us-citizen-with-espionage%2Farticleshow%2F102831781.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102831781.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ERussia%20has%20charged%20a%20jailed%20U.S.%20citizen%20with%20espionage%2C%20state%20news%20agencies%20reported%2C%20upping%20the%20pressure%20on%20U.S.%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20administration%20which%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20find%20a%20way%20to%20bring%20several%20detained%20citizens%20back%20home%20from%20Russia.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussia-charges-jaile