3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20started%20with%2030%20farmers%20in%202017%2C%20Adithi%20Millets%20has%20grown%20its%20farmer%20base%20to%20over%20200%20and%20has%20a%20turnover%20of%20Rs%202%20crore.%20The%20venture%20empowers%20farmers%20to%20grow%20millets%2C%20expand%20their%20marketing%20facility%2C%20trade%20with%20corporates%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESomashekar%20works%20across%20seven%20villages%20in%20three%20districts%20of%20Kurnool.%20The%20farmers%20from%20Tadakana%2C%20Ulinda%20Konda%2C%20Bhudidha%2C%20Nagalpuram%2C%20etc%20are%20all%20part%20of%20the%20association.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Millets%20to%20Millions%E2%80%99%3A%20founded%20on%20this%20philosophy%2C%20Adithi%20Millets%20is%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20spread%20the%20love%20and%20knowledge%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F313382%2Ftelangana-millet-man-led-millet-revolution-helped-dalit-women-earn-pv-satheesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethese%20superfoods%3C%2Fa%3E%20among%20the%20masses.%20On%20asking%20why%20he%20chose%20millets%2C%20he%20says%20that%20millets%20are%20very%20healthy%20and%20a%20great%20addition%20to%20everyone%E2%80%99s%20diet.%20Moreover%2C%20%E2%80%9Cmillets%20are%20easy%20to%20grow%2C%20which%20means%20farmers%20need%20not%20take%20huge%20loans%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Ffarming-2-1692018694.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22208%20farmers%20in%20seven%20villages%20of%20Kurnool%20are%20associated%20with%20Adithi%20Millets%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Ffarming-2-1692018694.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Ffarming-2-1692018694-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F