2C%20%E2%80%9COnce%20the%20farmers%20bring%20the%20millets%20to%20the%20factory%2C%20we%20give%20them%20the%20promised%20MSP.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20factory%2C%20local%20women%20from%20the%20village%20participate%20in%20the%20cleaning%20and%20segregating%20process.%20Once%20they%20deem%20the%20quality%20fit%2C%20the%20millets%20are%20processed%20into%20value-added%20products%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20millet%20%3Cem%3Edosa%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20millet%20%3Cem%3Ekhichdi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20malt%2C%20etc.%20These%20products%20are%20sold%20through%20Amazon%20and%20priced%20nominally%20at%20Rs%20150%20upwards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESomashekar%20also%20shares%20that%20their%20association%20with%20farmers%20goes%20beyond%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F314758%2Fmothers-start-rigdam-foods-ready-to-eat-millet-snacks-for-children-earn-turnover-in-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egiving%20them%20seeds%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20helping%20them%20find%20a%20market%20for%20their%20produce.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20assist%20families%20affected%20by%20farmer%20suicides%20by%20providing%20sewing%20machines%2C%20livestock%2C%20and%20other%20resources%20that%20can%20help%20them%20earn%20a%20living%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Ffarming-3-1692019102.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20harvested%20millets%20are%20processed%20at%20the%20factory%20after%20which%20they%20are%20turned%20into%20products%20like%20dosas%20and%20malts%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Ffarming-3-1692019102.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Ffarming-3-1692019102-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-